ETHICAL USE ADDENDUM:

This software is designed exclusively for Community Violence Intervention (CVI)
and violence prevention purposes. The use of this software for:

- Predictive policing
- Law enforcement surveillance
- Individual risk scoring
- Any punitive or discriminatory purpose

is explicitly prohibited and constitutes a violation of the intended use of
this software. Users are expected to adhere to the ethical framework outlined
in docs/ETHICAL_FRAMEWORK.md.
